Quetzalcoatl:

"It's seems that I have problems to transform... No I did it" said 
the male while he revealed for first time his robot form. 
Quetzalcoatl was without doubt the ugliest robot in trasformers' 
universe. He was shot but his arms was pretty large, his body was 
skinny and he walked hunched in robot mode.

His trasn formation to robot mode was similar to Airazor, bu his 
large wings was useful to fly in robot and beast mode.

When Quetzalcoatl saw his robot mode he felt ashamed for his own 
ugliness and covered hikmself with his wings while he walked towards 
the darknest place of the lab.
